description:
Don't know much about fashion but want to start? Love fashion and want to share? This is a group for EVERYONE  who is interested in fashion and style, for daily life.

We are gathering people with passion about fashion, beauty, quality life, and do something fun together (not targeting the fashion professionals, but you are more than welcome =). 

Fashion is not only about dressing, but also eating, drinking, traveling, working, living, etc. Fashion is an attitude!

description:
Hej Stockholm, We are TPH, an app dedicated to vintage clothes. From last collection 2013 or Lacoste in the 80's, we provide you with unique pieces from the past into your future. It's not because your budget is too small that you need to live on pasta to be the stylish one. As a fashion company, we think that mode and Instagram are strongly linked in 2016.

We are at the beginning of our start-up journey and like every one else we have some problematics.

So, we want to exchange about our app, vintage, fashion and of course Instagram.

We invite Influencers and names of the fashion world to join our Meetups.


TPH : <br>www.thepastahaters.com <br>@ThePastaHaters (Instagram)

category.name: fashion/beauty
description: Hi guys and girls, Any entrepreneurial designers that have computer-aided design and graphics editing software out there , I am interested in putting people together to discuss and help each other to over come whatever problems are holding you back from getting your fashion line out there. I want to create a COMMUNITY that pools our skills and knowledge so WE are in control,that goes from from pricing in China to who can make and source different materials every aspect is to be controlled by us, helping each other to lower production costs etc, I want to be able for us all to tap into everyone's different skill set to help each other and create the best environment and breeding ground for new startups, or indeed for established fashion houses. This is a talent pool to help each other, to bind us in a goal to get our creations on sale in stores at any cost, this is where the next generation of entrepreneurs are going to come from, Our ideas and determination will start a movement to make it easier for both the designers and the computer and editing people to work on collaborations together pulling from this same talent pool with the soul aim to get a garment or that cool pair of jeans etc, or any ones creation to market.I am just starting on my road to start a brand now too. I just moved to Ostermalm, Stockholm from Dublin Ireland, and am in the process of creating a brand,but I need help as everyone does, I need my designs to go from paper to auto cad,so that the skill set I need with all dimensions etc. So lets all become a community to reach out and help each other. My background is in International business and International export,I have just had some great meetings in the Stockholm chamber of commerce and have more meetings scheduled.E mail is heritagedissent@gmail.com
name: Stockholm fashion design community,for those with passion

category.name: fashion/beauty
description:
Hi everyone!

I'm a hair and makeup artist specializing in wedding, glamour, fashion and editorial. In my years of work I come across alot of women who want to learn more about hair and makeup techniques, but how and where to do this? So, I thought this might be a great chance to start a meetup where I can share my knowledge and we can help each other to learn, look great have fun and feel our best.

This meetup is for everyone interested in learning or mastering different techniques in makeup and or hair(we can gage interest), who want to meet new people and make new friends. <br>All skill levels, ages are welcome. I speak both swedish and english so don't be shy.

<br>IF there is enough interest then I can look at the next steps of when and where to meetup. There may be a small cost if we need to rent a space. <br>What do you think? Any budding MUA's out there?? <br>Best, <br>Victoria
name: Malmö Makeup Meetup

It's not because your budget is too small that you need to live on pasta to be the stylish one. As a fashion company, we think that mode and Instagram are strongly linked in 2016.

So, we want to exchange about our app, vintage, fashion and of course Instagram.

We invite Influencers and names of the fashion world to join our Meetups.


TPH : <br>www.thepastahaters.com <br>@ThePastaHaters (Instagram)

category.name: fashion/beauty
description: Hi guys and girls, Any entrepreneurial designers that have computer-aided design and graphics editing software out there , I am interested in putting people together to discuss and help each other to over come whatever problems are holding you back from getting your fashion line out there. I want to create a COMMUNITY that pools our skills and knowledge so WE are in control,that goes from from pricing in China to who can make and source different materials every aspect is to be controlled by us, helping each other to lower production costs etc, I want to be able for us all to tap into everyone's different skill set to help each other and create the best environment and breeding ground for new startups, or indeed for established fashion houses. This is a talent pool to help each other, to bind us in a goal to get our creations on sale in stores at any cost, this is where the next generation of entrepreneurs are going to come from, Our ideas and determination will start a movement to make it easier for both the designers and the computer and editing people to work on collaborations together pulling from this same talent pool with the soul aim to get a garment or that cool pair of jeans etc, or any ones creation to market.I am just starting on my road to start a brand now too. I just moved to Ostermalm, Stockholm from Dublin Ireland, and am in the process of creating a brand,but I need help as everyone does, I need my designs to go from paper to auto cad,so that the skill set I need with all dimensions etc. So lets all become a community to reach out and help each other. My background is in International business and International export,I have just had some great meetings in the Stockholm chamber of commerce and have more meetings scheduled.E mail is heritagedissent@gmail.com
name: Stockholm fashion design community,for those with passion

description:
Hi everyone!

category.name: fashion/beauty
description: Hi guys and girls, Any entrepreneurial designers that have computer-aided design and graphics editing software out there , I am interested in putting people together to discuss and help each other to over come whatever problems are holding you back from getting your fashion line out there. I want to create a COMMUNITY that pools our skills and knowledge so WE are in control,that goes from from pricing in China to who can make and source different materials every aspect is to be controlled by us, helping each other to lower production costs etc, I want to be able for us all to tap into everyone's different skill set to help each other and create the best environment and breeding ground for new startups, or indeed for established fashion houses. This is a talent pool to help each other, to bind us in a goal to get our creations on sale in stores at any cost, this is where the next generation of entrepreneurs are going to come from, Our ideas and determination will start a movement to make it easier for both the designers and the computer and editing people to work on collaborations together pulling from this same talent pool with the soul aim to get a garment or that cool pair of jeans etc, or any ones creation to market.I am just starting on my road to start a brand now too. I just moved to Ostermalm, Stockholm from Dublin Ireland, and am in the process of creating a brand,but I need help as everyone does, I need my designs to go from paper to auto cad,so that the skill set I need with all dimensions etc. So lets all become a community to reach out and help each other. My background is in International business and International export,I have just had some great meetings in the Stockholm chamber of commerce and have more meetings scheduled.E mail is heritagedissent@gmail.com
name: Stockholm fashion design community,for those with passion

description:
Hej Stockholm, We are TPH, an app dedicated to vintage clothes. From last collection 2013 or Lacoste in the 80's, we provide you with unique pieces from the past into your future. It's not because your budget is too small that you need to live on pasta to be the stylish one. As a fashion company, we think that mode and Instagram are strongly linked in 2016.

We are at the beginning of our start-up journey and like every one else we have some problematics.

So, we want to exchange about our app, vintage, fashion and of course Instagram.

We invite Influencers and names of the fashion world to join our Meetups.


TPH : <br>www.thepastahaters.com <br>@ThePastaHaters (Instagram)

category.name: fashion/beauty
description: Hi guys and girls, Any entrepreneurial designers that have computer-aided design and graphics editing software out there , I am interested in putting people together to discuss and help each other to over come whatever problems are holding you back from getting your fashion line out there. I want to create a COMMUNITY that pools our skills and knowledge so WE are in control,that goes from from pricing in China to who can make and source different materials every aspect is to be controlled by us, helping each other to lower production costs etc, I want to be able for us all to tap into everyone's different skill set to help each other and create the best environment and breeding ground for new startups, or indeed for established fashion houses. This is a talent pool to help each other, to bind us in a goal to get our creations on sale in stores at any cost, this is where the next generation of entrepreneurs are going to come from, Our ideas and determination will start a movement to make it easier for both the designers and the computer and editing people to work on collaborations together pulling from this same talent pool with the soul aim to get a garment or that cool pair of jeans etc, or any ones creation to market.I am just starting on my road to start a brand now too. I just moved to Ostermalm, Stockholm from Dublin Ireland, and am in the process of creating a brand,but I need help as everyone does, I need my designs to go from paper to auto cad,so that the skill set I need with all dimensions etc. So lets all become a community to reach out and help each other. My background is in International business and International export,I have just had some great meetings in the Stockholm chamber of commerce and have more meetings scheduled.E mail is heritagedissent@gmail.com
name: Stockholm fashion design community,for those with passion

description:
Don't know much about fashion but want to start? Love fashion and want to share? This is a group for EVERYONE  who is interested in fashion and style, for daily life.

We are gathering people with passion about fashion, beauty, quality life, and do something fun together (not targeting the fashion professionals, but you are more than welcome =). 

Fashion is not only about dressing, but also eating, drinking, traveling, working, living, etc. Fashion is an attitude!

category.name: fashion/beauty
description: Hi guys and girls, Any entrepreneurial designers that have computer-aided design and graphics editing software out there , I am interested in putting people together to discuss and help each other to over come whatever problems are holding you back from getting your fashion line out there. I want to create a COMMUNITY that pools our skills and knowledge so WE are in control,that goes from from pricing in China to who can make and source different materials every aspect is to be controlled by us, helping each other to lower production costs etc, I want to be able for us all to tap into everyone's different skill set to help each other and create the best environment and breeding ground for new startups, or indeed for established fashion houses. This is a talent pool to help each other, to bind us in a goal to get our creations on sale in stores at any cost, this is where the next generation of entrepreneurs are going to come from, Our ideas and determination will start a movement to make it easier for both the designers and the computer and editing people to work on collaborations together pulling from this same talent pool with the soul aim to get a garment or that cool pair of jeans etc, or any ones creation to market.I am just starting on my road to start a brand now too. I just moved to Ostermalm, Stockholm from Dublin Ireland, and am in the process of creating a brand,but I need help as everyone does, I need my designs to go from paper to auto cad,so that the skill set I need with all dimensions etc. So lets all become a community to reach out and help each other. My background is in International business and International export,I have just had some great meetings in the Stockholm chamber of commerce and have more meetings scheduled.E mail is heritagedissent@gmail.com
name: Stockholm fashion design community,for those with passion

description:
Hej Stockholm, We are TPH, an app dedicated to vintage clothes. From last collection 2013 or Lacoste in the 80's, we provide you with unique pieces from the past into your future. It's not because your budget is too small that you need to live on pasta to be the stylish one. As a fashion company, we think that mode and Instagram are strongly linked in 2016.

We are at the beginning of our start-up journey and like every one else we have some problematics.

So, we want to exchange about our app, vintage, fashion and of course Instagram.

We invite Influencers and names of the fashion world to join our Meetups.


TPH : <br>www.thepastahaters.com <br>@ThePastaHaters (Instagram)

category.name: fashion/beauty
description:
Hi everyone!

I'm a hair and makeup artist specializing in wedding, glamour, fashion and editorial. In my years of work I come across alot of women who want to learn more about hair and makeup techniques, but how and where to do this? So, I thought this might be a great chance to start a meetup where I can share my knowledge and we can help each other to learn, look great have fun and feel our best.

This meetup is for everyone interested in learning or mastering different techniques in makeup and or hair(we can gage interest), who want to meet new people and make new friends. <br>All skill levels, ages are welcome. I speak both swedish and english so don't be shy.

<br>IF there is enough interest then I can look at the next steps of when and where to meetup. There may be a small cost if we need to rent a space. <br>What do you think? Any budding MUA's out there?? <br>Best, <br>Victoria
